    "text": "Finally getting to work on beagle again. I was able to get some Cffi working. So here you see a simple sdl application and a socket server on a background thread. I made a quick vs code extension that sends the contents of a buffer to this socket and the code evals. Now I have a quick and simple live coding setup. Here I just invoke a function, but you can redefine functions as well. I need to work on live redefinition of structs and all sorts of bugs and edge cases. But it's pretty exciting to see some real stuff working!",
